subject: Coaches and Managers
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Running back LaMichael James and quarterback Jeremiah Masoli, two of Oregon’s top players, entered guilty pleas in separate cases Friday and awaited word on their future with the Ducks.
snippet: Running back LaMichael James and quarterback Jeremiah Masoli, two of Oregon’s top players, entered guilty pleas in separate cases Friday and awaited word on their future with the Ducks.
